<i> were these cool</i>
<i> recurve-style bayonets.</i>

03:37.843 --> 03:39.551
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

03:39.595 --> 03:41.428
- The design I'm going
for is going to be

03:41.472 --> 03:43.513
an old-fashioned
spear point dagger.

