<i> And I'm going to put a fuller</i>
<i> in the inside,</i>

03:47.144 --> 03:49.561
<i> mainly because with the fuller</i>
<i> it creates less drag.</i>

03:49.605 --> 03:52.231
I planned on forging
a very simple guard

