- This piece of material
is used to being a spring,

04:46.287 --> 04:47.995
not being a blade.

04:48.038 --> 04:50.038
So you've got to get it
out of that form.

04:50.082 --> 04:52.457
- Well, if you get
the metal hot enough,

04:52.501 --> 04:54.042
then you'll get that reaction.

04:54.086 --> 04:58.797
- There we go.
- Mechanical advantage.

04:58.841 --> 05:00.132
- Just want to get it
straightened out real quick.

05:00.175 --> 05:01.883
Coming to the hammer.

